A simple Play 2.1 (Scala) CRUD application using Anorm and Postgres. 

The db create table script is in etc/createTables.sql. 

In application.conf, the db url, userid and password needs to be set :

For example :
db.default.user=user
db.default.password=qwerty
db.default.url="jdbc:postgresql:playdb"
db.default.driver=org.postgresql.Driver

Also need to disbale evolution:
evolutionplugin=disabled


The context url of the application is http://localhost:9000/anormdemo1/  


